An Egyptian commando launched an assault on the kidnappers of the eleven tourists and their eight escorts kidnapped ten days ago.
I'm in Cairo.
The eleven European tourists and their eight Egyptian escorts held prisoner in the desert for ten days were returned on Monday afternoon, safe and sound, to the Egyptian capital.
In the morning, they were freed in Chad by an Egyptian commando.
